# OS files
.DS_Store*
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# --- Non-Unity tooling & planning artifacts (NOT needed to open or build the project) ---
# BMad Method framework + generated planning/implementation artifacts (GDD, epics, stories, sprint status)
/_bmad/
/_bmad-output/
# Claude Code: config, skills, and project guidance
/.claude/
/CLAUDE.md
# Agent definitions (BMad/GDS agents authored under .github/agents — not GitHub Actions CI)
/.agents/
/.github/agents/
# Source/staging art — raw Blender (.blend) + master FBX + concept doc.
# These are the SOURCE files; the pieces actually used get imported into Assets/
# (which IS tracked). Kept out of git on purpose: the 214MB "game map .blend"
# exceeds GitHub's 100MB per-file limit. Version source art via Git LFS or external
# storage if it ever needs tracking.
/CAMERA GAME SHARED FOLDER/

# Unity crash-recovery backups (auto-created after an unexpected shutdown; not real content)
/Assets/_Recovery/
/Assets/_Recovery.meta
